{"title":"七月一日好时光  唱首山歌表心肠","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月一日好时光  唱首山歌表心肠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心心朝向共产党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月一日好时光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱首山歌表心肠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我今得到翻身日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远不忘共产党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（江西　袁兆兴）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葵花葵花金子黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朵朵开花像太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葵花就是万人心呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心心朝向共产党！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（川南）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腊梅开花朵朵新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席啊在北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那怕路隔千万里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民和您心连心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（江西遂川）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青松翠柏不怕雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹雨打不枯黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党好比松柏树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四季常青万年长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（江苏泰县）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信天游捎给毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南来的大雁北去的风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信天游捎给毛主席听；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山丹丹开花满山坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱陕北变成金银窝；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修起水渠打起埝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群群牛羊满山窜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进歌声飞满天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人力定要战胜天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信天游，不断头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今的生活不发愁；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝塔山高延水长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党是我们亲爹娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（陕西　郭桦）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端起饭碗想起党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张煎饼一碗汤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端起饭碗想起党；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都说爹娘亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党呀，胜过亲爹娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"片片乌云遮蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茫茫苦海没有边；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是党把俺来搭救，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳出苦海得温暖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面红旗迎风飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合作社来幸福道；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子一天比一天好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活步步得提高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起从前心里酸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常年吃菜把糠咽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入了社吃喝得改善，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴上香哟心里甜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半间破房四面风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下雨下雪冷冰冰；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今换上新瓦房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光普照暖烘烘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一件破袄片连片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全家几口合着穿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今生活变美了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿女打扮得花枝般。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（江苏丰县　赵家祥）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳的光芒万万丈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳红，太阳亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳的光芒万万丈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们如今俩太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个太阳不一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个太阳住北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个太阳挂天上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上的太阳暖身上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京的太阳暖心房。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（山东　郭澄清）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了共产党，河水往上淌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了共产党，水库修山上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了共产党，遍山果树长；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了共产党，山地庄稼强；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了共产党，牛羊满山岗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了共产党，家家有余粮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（山东）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠党不靠天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了共产党，岁岁庆丰年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要想更富裕，靠党不靠天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（浙江）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从共产党来掌舵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里荒山出草药，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九里坡前稻田多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个男子娶老婆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四川石砫）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩挑谷子喜洋洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担担谷子闪金光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光照在心坎上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里想起共产党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（湖北麻城）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一江溪水混混流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数千年来无人收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党的领导好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灌溉良田数百丘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四川叙永）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄花开靠东风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄花开靠东风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万道霞光满天红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瑶族翻身靠那个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全靠恩人毛泽东。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（湖南洞口瑶族）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京城里开着花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凉山深谷闻到香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京城头飘红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凉山山上映红光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（凉山彝族）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席来到了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天变了，地变了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看这水土也变了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往年还是干坝田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今一片水汪汪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮萍漂在水面上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像天上落下来的采云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿您像太阳一样长寿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（苗族）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}